        "Params": "{3: 'The withdrawal of the Ascendants does not signal the end of the war. The Corrupted, war machines left behind by the Ascendants, must still be cleansed.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
